%% ActivaClub - Promotions Broadcast Flow via SNS (EP-05)
%% Diagram 8 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant Manager
    participant Frontend
    participant PromotionsLambda
    participant DynamoDB as DynamoDB (PromotionsTable)
    participant SNS
    participant Members

    Manager->>Frontend: Create promotion + click "Difundir"
    Frontend->>PromotionsLambda: POST /v1/promotions/:id/broadcast
    PromotionsLambda->>DynamoDB: GetItem promotion
    PromotionsLambda->>SNS: Publish { topicArn, message, attributes: { membershipTier } }
    SNS-->>Members: Email / Push notification delivered to filtered subscribers
    PromotionsLambda->>DynamoDB: UpdateItem promotion (broadcastAt = now)
    PromotionsLambda-->>Frontend: 200 { broadcastAt }
